## Navigation System
- **State Management**: React state for current section tracking
- **URL Updates**: Uses window.history.pushState for clean URLs without page reload
- **Section Handling**: Home, Projects, Products, Services, Contact
- **Mobile Navigation**: Sliding dropdown with fade animation, full-width active states
- **Dark Mode**: Inverted text colors for active navigation options

## SwipeableImages Features
- **Swipeable**: Touch swipe on mobile, mouse drag on desktop
- **Horizontal Layout**: Images arranged horizontally with smooth transitions
- **Manual Controls**: Dot navigation for direct image access
- **Responsive Images**: Desktop (1200x500, 85% quality) and mobile (800x400, 70% quality) optimized versions
- **Height**: 500px desktop, 400px mobile for better visual impact
- **Performance**: Significantly reduced file sizes (7.3MB → 101KB desktop, 33KB mobile for largest image)

## Content Layout
- **Data-Driven**: All content loaded from JSON files for easy management
- **Two Layout Types**: 
  - **Two-Column Layout**: Home section with 1:2 ratio (heading:content)
  - **Regular Layout**: Services, Contact, Products, Projects with h3 + p structure
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with single column on mobile
- **Line Break Support**: Headings respect \n characters for multi-line titles
- **Unselectable**: All content is non-selectable for clean interaction

## Dark Mode Support
- **Automatic Detection**: Uses prefers-color-scheme media query
- **Color Inversion**: Active navigation options use inverted text colors
- **Background Colors**: Same color palette maintained across themes
- **Text Contrast**: Black text on colored backgrounds in dark mode

